anger restated." Am J Psychiatry 135 (1978): 1097-100[16] Moreau A, Jones BD, Banno V "Chronic central anticholinergic toxicity in manic depressive illness mimicking dementia." Can J Psychiatry 31 (1986): 339-41', 1767363026);
